th\neasier handling of modeling alternatives. Sensitivity analysis, measures of\ngoodness of fit and model choice are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Jan 2014 19:06:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Feb 2014 12:47:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-25"}
