 too small depending on the star formation feedback implementation.\nKinematical misalignments match the observations only qualitatively. The main\npoint of conflict is that nearly all simulated FRs and a large fraction of all\nsimulated SRs host corotating HI. This establishes the HI properties of ETGs as\na novel challenge to simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Jan 2014 13:27:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
